sentences: Taj Stansberry (born in Oakland, California, United States) is an American director and photographer, known for his music videos with artists such as Rihanna, J Lo, Usher, Ne-Yo, John Legend, Young Jeezy, Ludacris, Keyshia Cole, Swizz Beatz, Eve, Wale and Big Sean.
He is currently developing a few feature projects as well.
Today he is with Happy Place Productions under the umbrella of his TPK (The Popular Kid) brand.
